# bell7; sleep 45.7 # //      14.3313s round medium
# bell8; sleep 49.7 # //      10.2877s round medium resonant
# bell9; sleep 39.8 # //      20.1896s ding
# bell10; sleep 54.9 # //     5.1338s ding resonant
